      <title>诺曼·李尔 (Norman Lear) 去世，享年 101 岁，曾制作过一些严肃话题的搞笑情景喜剧</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2023/12/06/334890639/norman-lear-who-made-funny-sitcoms-about-serious-topics-dies-at-101</link>
